# API Rules
- Layered: routes → controllers → services → repositories (Prisma).
- Validate all inputs with zod middleware using @trendywheels/validators.
- Log with pino structured JSON. Never log PII.
- Auth: JWT RS256. Rate limit: 100 req/min/user via Redis.
- Central error handler → Sentry.
- Background jobs: BullMQ on Redis.
